snippet.title: Amber Heard AKA Mera looks dazzling at the premiere of Aquaman
snippet.description:
They've been together since 2005 and share two children. And Jason Momoa, 39, and wife Lisa Bonet, 51, looked more in love than ever at the Hollywood premiere of Aquaman on Wednesday. The couple shared a passionate kiss on the red carpet outside the TCL Chinese Theater.
